---
layout: base.njk
---
{% from "icons.njk" import categoryIcon %}
<article class="article">
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": {{ title | dump | safe }},
    "description": {{ description | dump | safe }},
    "datePublished": "{{ date | htmlDateString }}",
    "author": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "{{ site.name }}"
    },
    "publisher": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "{{ site.name }}"
    }
  }
  </script>

  <nav class="breadcrumbs">
    <a href="/">Artículos</a> <span class="sep">›</span> <span class="badge">{{ category }}</span>
  </nav>

  <span class="icon-bubble icon-bubble-lg">{{ categoryIcon(category) }}</span>
  <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
  <p class="article-date">Actualizado: {{ date | readableDate }}</p>

  <div class="article-body">
    {{ content | safe }}
  </div>

  <p class="disclaimer">
    Este contenido es informativo y no constituye asesoría legal ni migratoria.
    Verifica siempre los requisitos y montos vigentes en las fuentes oficiales citadas
    (USCIS, IRCC, Cancillería de Colombia o Migración Colombia) antes de tomar decisiones.
  </p>
</article>
